sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Database

    Client->>API: POST /carts/{cartId}/items (AddItemRequest)
    API->>Database: SELECT id FROM carts WHERE id = $1
    Database-->>API: carts row (or not found)
    alt cart not found
        API-->>Client: 404 Not Found (ProblemDetail)
    else cart found
        API->>Database: INSERT INTO cart_items (id, cart_id, product_id, quantity, unit_price, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (...) RETURNING *
        Database-->>API: new cart_items row
        API->>Database: UPDATE carts SET updated_at = NOW() WHERE id = $1
        API-->>Client: 201 Created (CartItem)
    end
